outputs.output_descr: The project aims to improve the response capacity of the Government of Liberia and its partners to the epidemic of viral hemorrhagic fever Ebola.

project_descr: The UN country team led by WHO, and the UN Mission in Liberia (UNMIL) is working closely with development partners including international Non-Governmental Organizations to support the Government of Liberia  (GoL) to bring the epidemic under control.
